{"id":177874,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-201197/","date":"2011-09-08T00:30:38Z","modified":"2011-09-08T02:56:49Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐  2011/9/7","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/sep/06/chinese-activist-daughter-barred-school\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国活动家的女儿被禁止上学</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——据介绍，不仅陈光诚本人被软禁，连他的</span></span><span><span>6</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁女儿也被禁止离开家去上学。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.telegraph.co.uk/news/peterfoster/100103309/the-law-in-china-sometimes-brutal-sometimes-brilliant/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">治</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：时而野蛮，时而精妙</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——记者以盲人律师陈光诚的女儿不能上学和湖北法官调解纠纷为例，介绍了中国的法治现状</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">维基解密：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.wikileaks.org/cable/2009/11/09BEIJING3046.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">胡锦涛来拜年</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国使馆的一份电报，记述了中国地方干部是如何准备胡锦涛到农村走访的。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/07/world/asia/07hongkong.html?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚视高管因误报江泽民去世而辞职</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——误报事件发生两个月之后，两名亚视高管辞职。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/09/07/chinas-premier-sees-inflation-as-top-priority-or-does-he/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国总理是否真的把通胀作为第一要务</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？——温家宝最近的一些言论显示他没决定到底是要控制物价还是要鼓励增长</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21528212\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">新中产阶级的崛起</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的空气中弥漫着造反的气息，但与中东不同的是，中国中产阶级的目标不是推翻现政府。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基国际和平基金会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/publications/index.cfm?fa=view&#038;id=45483&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+carnegie%2Fchina+%28DC+-+Region+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对从现在到</span>2020<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年的展望</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的居民消费占</span></span><span><span>GDP</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">比例继续下降，债务水平继续攀升，增长速度到</span></span><span><span>2013</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">～</span></span><span><span>14</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年大幅下降</span></span><span><span>…</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/09/06/taiwan-opposition-leader-advocates-dumping-old-1992-consensus-on-china/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">台湾反对党领袖呼吁抛弃老的“中国共识”</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——蔡英文要取消</span></span><span><span>92</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">共识，发展台湾共识，大陆的反应是“毫不现实、不可接受”</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《洛杉矶时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/asia/la-fg-china-foreign-news-20110905,0,2129313.story?track=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的官方媒体如履薄冰</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他们在报道国际大事时，既要让其政治领导人满意，又要应对越来越成熟的公众。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《亚洲时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.atimes.com/atimes/China/MI07Ad01.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国刑法修正案错失良机</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年前开始修订时，人们对其寄予厚望，但是最新出台的刑法修正案却有失法制精神。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110906/bs_nm/us_china_economy\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国开始调整经济事务负责人</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span>18</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">大的政治交接还未开始，经济领域的高官已开始调整。这是路透社对财政部和银行等部门负责人变动的预测</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/07/world/asia/07china.html?_r=1\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国称将加强对海外军火销售的控制</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——外交部发言人在记者会上做出上述表示，但没有提供具体措施</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约客》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/evanosnos/2011/09/chinas-iceland-moment.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的冰岛时刻</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国企业家黄怒波购买冰岛土地一事，让人想起当年日本手握巨额外汇，到海外购买土地和房产的情景。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">数字茶博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://digicha.com/index.php/2011/09/could-regulatory-winter-be-coming-for-china-internet-investors/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国互联网投资者是否面临法规严冬？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——近期种种迹象表明政府希望严管互联网和社交媒体，外国投资者很可能会被排挤掉</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110907/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_oil_spill\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国国务院下令调查康菲漏油事件</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国海洋管理部门指责康菲没有按时清理泄漏原油，国务院要求彻底调查漏油原因和造成的损失。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-09-05/conoco-defends-china-spill-response-in-face-of-public-wrath.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">康菲公司面对公众的愤怒为自己辩解</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国官方媒体猛烈抨击康菲，而康菲则自称已全力堵漏清理，并无拖延与瞒报</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>BBC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-pacific-14802394\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的白皮书保证和平崛起</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国政府发布此文件提出对中国未来几十年发展的构想，但是对于如何实现这些目标却并未提供具体措施</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/09/06/red_dawn\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">红色黎明</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——为什么美国应该欢迎中国的经济崛起，而不是害怕它</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/09/06/how-china-sees-middle-east/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国如何看待中东？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国官方依然坚持和平共处五项原则，但学者们对于中东变化的观点则和西方主流的看法类似。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲观察哨：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.asiasentinel.com/index.php?option=com_content&#038;task=view&#038;id=3718&#038;Itemid=225\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">印度的对华贸易收支问题</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——面对快速增加的对华贸易赤字，印度国大党政府计划采取行动加以抗衡</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《基督教科学箴言报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Africa/Africa-Monitor/2011/0906/West-Africa-Rising-Nigeria-shifting-currency-reserves-from-dollars-to-Chinese-yuan?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+feeds%2Fworld+%28Christian+Science+Monitor+%7C+World%25\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">西非崛起</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——随着中国作为贸易伙伴的重要性增加，尼日利亚将储备货币从美元改为人民币。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21528262\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">被束缚的资本主义</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在中国，政府与企业的关系非常复杂，私有企业是改革之后才出现的，但政府并不情愿放弃管理权</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/09/06/cant-get-a-bank-loan-chinese-state-owned-companies-happy-to-help-out/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">从银行贷不到款？国营企业可以帮你</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——政府的反通胀措施，使得私企难以得到银行贷款，而国企却把用不着的闲钱拿来放高利贷。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业内幕》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/chinese-corporate-bonds-are-tanking-like-its-2008-2011-9?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+businessinsider+%28Business+Insider%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国企业债券大跌</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——八月份中国企业债券下跌</span></span><span><span>1.5%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，出现自</span></span><span><span>2008</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年以来的最大跌幅。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><b><span> </span></b></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《单位》博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.danwei.com/opening-the-door-to-american-universities-with-lies/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">靠谎言打开美国大学的大门</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“如果人们存在中国学生申请时弄虚作假的印象，这会有损于中国的形象。而现实正是如此。”</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/08/world/asia/08iht-letter08.html?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国法律将让离婚妇女无家可归</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——根据最高法院对婚姻法的解释，许多中国妇女发现自己的配偶一夜之间成了自己房东。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>MSNBC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://behindthewall.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2011/09/07/7647012-c-section-baby-boom-in-china\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的剖腹产热潮</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在北京，超过一半的婴儿是剖腹产。有些孕妇是遵照医嘱而剖，有些则是为了给孩子将来上学选个好日子。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/09/07/how-the-hukou-system-creates-aids-villages/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">户口是如何导致艾滋村的</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国医疗体系对艾滋病人提供几乎免费的药物，但这是和病人户口所在地挂钩的。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《基督教科学箴言报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Global-News/2011/0907/China-s-richest-citizens-Soda-and-the-Internet-help-fuel-the-growing-Hurun-Rich-List?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+feeds%2Fworld+%28Christian+Science+Monitor+%7C+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国最富者</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——软饮料和互联网让胡润富豪榜的名单越来越长</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110907/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_rich_exodus\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国富人最想做的是：离开中国</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——共产党以提高人民生活水平来换取执政合法性，可是富裕起来的人们却想方设法要逃离。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/scene/2011/09/06/china-to-overtake-japan-in-luxury-demand-hsbc-says/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国奢侈品需求量今年将超过日本</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——面子文化是中国成为世界最大奢侈品消费国的原因之一</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；译者的音频博客已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；下载更新需翻墙。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-3076159879665943192?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[8840,15095]}